dav2d is an AV2 cross-platform decoder,
open-source, and focused on speed and correctness.
It is based on popular dav1d decoder.
The goal of this project is to provide a decoder
for most platforms, and achieve the highest speed
possible to overcome the temporary lack of AV2
hardware decoder.It will support all features from
AV2, including all subsampling and bit-depth
parameters.
